{"title":"外食一覧","virttualPath":null,"html":"<div class=\"markdown-body\"><h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-外食一覧\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E5%A4%96%E9%A3%9F%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>外食一覧</h1>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-ルール\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E3%83%AB%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AB\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>ルール</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>写真を添えて店名と場所、時期だけ書く。</li>\n<li><strong>負の評価は明示して決して書かない。</strong></li>\n<li>特別に良い評価だけ書く。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-とんかつ系\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E3%81%A8%E3%82%93%E3%81%8B%E3%81%A4%E7%B3%BB\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>とんかつ系</h2>\n<p>とんかつナンバーワンは『かつぞう』。量より質。ひじき梅ごはんも絶妙にうまい。</p>\n<p>2019/10 かつぞう [金沢]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/97f5a584fa8bc284bc6a0d4418ba7236.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/97f5a584fa8bc284bc6a0d4418ba7236.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"かつぞう\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/10 とんとん亭 [金沢]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/9ad1793748c1956278a59241a00db9fc.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/9ad1793748c1956278a59241a00db9fc.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"とんとん\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/09 かつや [金沢]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/655a6a7bc25015ba46bbd510cf6534ef.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/655a6a7bc25015ba46bbd510cf6534ef.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"かつや\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/08 銭形 [新潟県糸魚川]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/7505bd12e7eb79e4d91b56be5b9608bb.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/7505bd12e7eb79e4d91b56be5b9608bb.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"銭形\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/08 とん八 [立山町] (<em>残念ながら 2020 年に閉業</em> 料理の上手なお袋の味だった。ほんとに残念。)</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/41b99a10b6ee48537013841c6e80beb3.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/41b99a10b6ee48537013841c6e80beb3.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"とん八\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/07 富金豚 [金沢フォーラス]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/50eb568cf249cf05c9c2f4ef447b5f9a.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/50eb568cf249cf05c9c2f4ef447b5f9a.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"富金豚\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2018/04 ファミリーレストラン堀井 [高岡市]</p>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"image/5f4aed46f6e19119493962bfe41f4e01.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/5f4aed46f6e19119493962bfe41f4e01.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"ファミレス堀井\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-ラーメン\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E3%83%A9%E3%83%BC%E3%83%A1%E3%83%B3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>ラーメン</h2>\n<p>金沢近郊で好きな順に、1: 中華そば響 2: 魂心屋(金沢諸江) 3: 豚蔵(せせらぎ通り) 4: 吟とん(東金沢)</p>\n<p>金沢近郊で今一番好きなのが白山市乾町あたりの中華そば響。逆方向なのでなかなか行けない。煮干しダシとチャーシューがたまらない。<br>\nどハマリしたのが家系の魂心屋。行きすぎてさすがに飽きた。<br>\nめったに行けない氷見の貪瞋痴は特別パターンでラーメンという分類は適切ではない気がする。</p>\n<p>2017/11 中華そば響 [野々市]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/c33893ee8804cd6a97a3136860e99014.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/c33893ee8804cd6a97a3136860e99014.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2020/12 かんか [金沢]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/26703274ec4ce2ff37b209101adfa138.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/26703274ec4ce2ff37b209101adfa138.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2020/10 らぁ麺 大和 [金沢西側]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/4fa552e41b3ffb71c77aa73e190a9886.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/4fa552e41b3ffb71c77aa73e190a9886.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/12 吟とん [東金沢]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/5c19a6ffef8152a29459c51168c380ac.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/5c19a6ffef8152a29459c51168c380ac.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/10 ひろまる [福光]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/d889cf2504293b1938fecb893a5f0577.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/d889cf2504293b1938fecb893a5f0577.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/07 豚蔵 [金沢]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/1846cbe67b62bef14d3be0d3f79e0905.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/1846cbe67b62bef14d3be0d3f79e0905.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"豚蔵\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/09 魂心屋 [金沢]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/7a20b45591b362e2b1872a7df17b7196.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/7a20b45591b362e2b1872a7df17b7196.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"魂心屋\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/08 白鷺 [金沢]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/3d24dee4793a0ff912552ec127cfc6ae.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/3d24dee4793a0ff912552ec127cfc6ae.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"白鷺\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/12 吉宗 [金沢駅前]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/f7ed0043970293a1ee4f1ac0b8ab891d.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/f7ed0043970293a1ee4f1ac0b8ab891d.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/07 吟とん [東金沢]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/265dd0a314a17e17537261dc4c73fe4f.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/265dd0a314a17e17537261dc4c73fe4f.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"吟とん\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/06 南車 [飛騨高山]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/4e696795612998c0d2e0898d7d0c6bb8.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/4e696795612998c0d2e0898d7d0c6bb8.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"南車\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2018/04 貪瞋痴 [富山県氷見市]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/4233c9232968154a1be3931d81122431.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/4233c9232968154a1be3931d81122431.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2016/09 富山キラリ [富山県射水市]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/bb7435459004a5d7ed93b9cee58f8fd3.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/bb7435459004a5d7ed93b9cee58f8fd3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n\n\n<p>2016/04 神楽 [金沢 寺町]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/6a08f82904b44254179b80e71835cc72.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/6a08f82904b44254179b80e71835cc72.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-肉\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E8%82%89\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>肉</h2>\n<p>2020/02 牛タン食堂 [金沢中央卸売市場通り]</p>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"image/1848f1a8309db11bdff55c0c4c074e02.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/1848f1a8309db11bdff55c0c4c074e02.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/38ef4e609ed58d07b3470ba03f829694.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/38ef4e609ed58d07b3470ba03f829694.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/03 肉食堂 [金沢中央卸売市場通り]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/efb240312cf9ea291c2aabb88b5de394.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/efb240312cf9ea291c2aabb88b5de394.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-飯-全般\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E9%A3%AF-%E5%85%A8%E8%88%AC\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>飯 (全般)</h2>\n<p>2018/02 円城 [南砺市福野]</p>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"image/2acd1d664ea7f2845eb86520c2c083f5.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/2acd1d664ea7f2845eb86520c2c083f5.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/ff031efce3cc6ec29bed1e882d1a44eb.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/ff031efce3cc6ec29bed1e882d1a44eb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/06 円城 [南砺市福野]</p>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"image/82eb3dc8f30d8ae815f25db165acdceb.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/82eb3dc8f30d8ae815f25db165acdceb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/b2a0ed5092ad401cac3a17764f934f2f.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/b2a0ed5092ad401cac3a17764f934f2f.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2020/09 どもん [七尾市中島町]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/46dbf133d4f7bd0f144ac6ef06d14618.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/46dbf133d4f7bd0f144ac6ef06d14618.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-中華台湾料理\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E4%B8%AD%E8%8F%AF%E5%8F%B0%E6%B9%BE%E6%96%99%E7%90%86\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>中華、台湾料理</h2>\n<p>遠いけど台湾菜館が一番好み。ここに写真上げてないけど、金沢なら高いけど菜香楼。</p>\n<p>2020/09 台湾菜館 [立山町]</p>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"image/0e6c297586fee3954f544d8f0865f107.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/0e6c297586fee3954f544d8f0865f107.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/2af5ac1ce1750ed03fa007904d369071.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/2af5ac1ce1750ed03fa007904d369071.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2020/09 白馬飯店 [長野県白馬村]</p>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"image/95d7385367c58bd9ded855d82878533a.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/95d7385367c58bd9ded855d82878533a.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/761fcced352b99bbc9c7165a602f65c2.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/761fcced352b99bbc9c7165a602f65c2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2020/08 小雪 [鶴来町]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/ff3a5c50360e0ea4a3135737699d4286.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/ff3a5c50360e0ea4a3135737699d4286.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/06 香林 [穴水]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/296b36042245fb6c1208bdd73dcba2a4.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/296b36042245fb6c1208bdd73dcba2a4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-洋食一般\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E6%B4%8B%E9%A3%9F%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>洋食一般</h2>\n<p>遠いけど一番好きなのが白馬の来夢来人。値段とボリュームが良心的。</p>\n<p>2020/09 来夢来人 [長野県白馬村]</p>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"image/d39803c7e712ae208a53d2b8af51002f.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/d39803c7e712ae208a53d2b8af51002f.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/36dfe52f8b31244dda499aa794d66997.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/36dfe52f8b31244dda499aa794d66997.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/08 鎌倉パスタ [金沢フォーラス]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/52e638bd2e82f54b32241421068baad8.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/52e638bd2e82f54b32241421068baad8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-蕎麦\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E8%95%8E%E9%BA%A6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>蕎麦</h2>\n<p>蕎麦正まつい [郡上八幡]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/36e643e1efd7f42d4a625501504fe825.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/36e643e1efd7f42d4a625501504fe825.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"蕎麦正まつい\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>そば神 [白馬村]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/1af64c955c7fc8cc65618dc360efa5a5.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/1af64c955c7fc8cc65618dc360efa5a5.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"そば神\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>そじ坊 [金沢駅中]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/add36116dd073685758f8345bbb31efd.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/add36116dd073685758f8345bbb31efd.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"そじ坊\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-寿司\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#%E5%AF%BF%E5%8F%B8\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>寿司</h2>\n<p>寿司はネタさえ新鮮ならとりあえずよい。握りがゆるい、値段不相応とかはあるけども。</p>\n<p>2020/12 すしのや [富山県氷見市]</p>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"image/6ba3469464e97fcba00dee26410fe92c.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/6ba3469464e97fcba00dee26410fe92c.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/2295ead46b7351472f3b23ec1f2e66cd.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/2295ead46b7351472f3b23ec1f2e66cd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2020/11 もりもり寿司 [宇出津]</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"image/2f5ee83ee6e150fc386e6e727923e03f.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/2f5ee83ee6e150fc386e6e727923e03f.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/c4214d467af7e0a599ca7b058a045593.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/c4214d467af7e0a599ca7b058a045593.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/86767d8940380ec55d7d29383373d0e3.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/86767d8940380ec55d7d29383373d0e3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/07 高尾 [穴水]</p>\n\n\n<p><a href=\"image/ceb121b64832ede35e07acfb5776874f.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/ceb121b64832ede35e07acfb5776874f.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/a5935239077d6dc01b0d4524fb92166e.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/a5935239077d6dc01b0d4524fb92166e.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2019/10 宝寿司 [宇出津]</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"image/8dca4794cea094a1e0e26a627c6f5ef1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/8dca4794cea094a1e0e26a627c6f5ef1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/185fda0429d5d5ec2eb8161044091963.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/185fda0429d5d5ec2eb8161044091963.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/25a52c0917f1aee3a166cac853ce4857.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/25a52c0917f1aee3a166cac853ce4857.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/7d8efbce0e9aab715347a6e612e1e669.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/7d8efbce0e9aab715347a6e612e1e669.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2018/08 西海丸 [富来町]</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"image/02d3ad28ef37d9d9be3015769bddadbb.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/02d3ad28ef37d9d9be3015769bddadbb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/03a54193238a5082a11d198f71b6f3c1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/03a54193238a5082a11d198f71b6f3c1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/b68e07c18ae3d056dcf7468454d56301.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/b68e07c18ae3d056dcf7468454d56301.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/f23098796f6714abb73da436ecc5f07c.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/f23098796f6714abb73da436ecc5f07c.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>2018/04 辰巳寿司 [七尾]</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"image/656b522896e9026eb759d161cd0992bb.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/656b522896e9026eb759d161cd0992bb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>2017/07 まつの [宇ノ気]</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"image/b27ddc22939a452de14bdfa6d236d8a6.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/b27ddc22939a452de14bdfa6d236d8a6.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"image/80bbcae9a2f5a6b0e712a57ebfbbfd70.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"image/80bbcae9a2f5a6b0e712a57ebfbbfd70.jpg\" alt=\"